
Copy settings.json to data, edit in your WiFi credentials & create a data
partition on your microcontroller. Edit in your TZ string for yout time zone. You
can probably find that here: 
https://github.com/esp8266/Arduino/blob/master/cores/esp8266/TZ.h

Copy User_Setup.h to TFT_eSPI directory. Edit this file as necessary for
the pins your controller uses for displays, sensors etc.
